  <span class="text-2xl font-bold">Helpful feedback should leave someone with a clearer understanding of their behaviour and a practical sense of what to do next.</span>
</div>

	
<h1 class="mb-5 text-4xl font-bold">Four qualities of helpful feedback</h1>


